		<article class="flex flex-col gap-3">
			<h2 class="border-b-2 pb-1 text-3xl">Skills</h2>

			<ul class="list-disc">
				<li>
					<span class="font-bold">Languages:</span> TypeScript, JavaScript, HTML, CSS, SQL, Python, Java,
					C#
