					<li>Co-managed a project and designed requested features.</li>
					<li>Refactored legacy code and migrated features to new technologies.</li>
				</ul>
			</section>

			<section class="flex flex-col gap-1">
				<div class="flex items-center">
					<div class="flex-1">
						<h3 class="text-xl font-extrabold">Research Professor</h3>
