				<div class="flex items-center">
					<div class="flex-1">
						<h3 class="text-xl font-extrabold">Web Development Co-Instructor</h3>
						<p>ECCI, University of Costa Rica</p>
					</div>
					<div class="text-right">
						<p>San José, Costa Rica</p>
						<p>Feb 2023 - Mar 2023</p>
					</div>
				</div>
				<ul class="list-disc">
					<li>Designed front end development workshop for 3 weeks.</li>
					<li>
						Taught HTML, CSS, JavaScript, frameworks, meta-frameworks, React, client side rendering,
