				<div class="flex items-center">
					<p class="flex-1">Python, YOLO, Deep Learning</p>
					<p>Mar 2023 - Present</p>
				</div>
				<ul class="list-disc">
					<li>
						Multidisciplinary effort (nutrition and computer science) to detect and classify
						unhealthy food ads
					</li>
					<li>Create an unhealthy food dataset</li>
					<li>Train different models using YOLOv8</li>
					<li>
						A paper was written to report preliminary results and it was published in CISTI'2023
					</li>
				</ul>
			</section>
		</article>

		<article class="flex flex-col gap-3">
			<h2 class="border-b-2 pb-1 text-3xl">Education/Certification</h2>

			<section class="flex flex-col gap-1">
				<h3 class="text-xl font-extrabold">AWS Certified Cloud Practitioner</h3>
				<div class="flex items-center">
					<p class="flex-1">Credential ID: 3NJ97G1B5NE41VC7</p>
					<p>2024</p>
				</div>
